#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3-32B-W4A4.md:1
msgid "Qwen3-32B-W4A4"
msgstr "Qwen3-32B-W4A4"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3-32B-W4A4.md:3
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "简介"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3-32B-W4A4.md:5
msgid ""
"W4A4 Flat Quantization is for better model compression and inference "
"efficiency on Ascend devices. And W4A4 is supported since `v0.11.0rc1`. "
"For modelslim, W4A4 is supported since `tag_MindStudio_8.2.RC1.B120_002`."
msgstr ""
"W4A4 Flat Quantization 旨在提升 Ascend 设备上的模型压缩和推理效率。W4A4 从 `v0.11.0rc1` 版本开始支持。"
"对于 modelslim，W4A4 从 `tag_MindStudio_8.2.RC1.B120_002` 版本开始支持。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3-32B-W4A4.md:8
